OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales is to return to
OL,7,Finternational travel by carrying out
OL,8,Fher first overseas royal visit since
OL,9,Fher cancer diagnosis.
OL,11,FKate, who revealed she was in
OL,12,Fremission at the start of last year,
OL,13,Fwill head to Italy next week on a solo
OL,14,Fworking trip with The Royal Foundation
OL,15,FCentre for Early Childhood.
OL,17,FIt is a major milestone for the future
OL,18,Fqueen and is her first extended
OL,19,Fofficial foreign trip in nearly three-
OL,20,Fand-a-half years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FAides to the princess shared how she
OL,7,Fwas "very much looking forward" to
OL,8,Fgetting back to international travel
OL,9,Fand said the visit was an important
OL,10,Fmoment in the expansion of the Centre
OL,11,Ffor Early Childhood's work on a global
OL,12,Fstage.
OL,14,FKate last carried out an official
OL,15,Foverseas visit in December 2022 when
OL,16,Fshe went to Boston, USA, with the
OL,17,FPrince of Wales for his Earthshot
OL,18,FPrize award ceremony.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FShe also undertook two brief trips to
OL,7,FMarseille, France, for the Rugby World
OL,8,FCup in the autumn of 2023, and went to
OL,9,Fthe Crown Prince of Jordan's wedding
OL,10,Fin Amman in June 2023 but these were
OL,11,Fnot considered by her royal household
OL,12,Fto be official foreign tours.
OL,14,FThe princess will visit the city of
OL,15,FReggio Emilia in northern Italy for
OL,16,Ftwo days from May 13 to May 14 to
OL,17,Ffocus on early years child development.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FDuring her European stay, Kate will
OL,7,Flearn more about the Reggio Emilia
OL,8,FApproach, an educational philosophy
OL,9,Fwhich focuses on the idea that
OL,10,Fchildren have the potential for self-
OL,11,Fdevelopment.
OL,13,FShe will also highlight the importance
OL,14,Fof nurturing environments and loving
OL,15,Frelationships to a child's development.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FA Kensington Palace spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"The princess is very much looking
OL,8,Fforward to visiting Italy next week
OL,9,Fand seeing first-hand how the Reggio
OL,10,FEmilia approach creates environments
OL,11,Fwhere nature and loving human
OL,12,Frelationships come together to support
OL,13,Fchildren's development.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,F"As the Centre for Early Childhood
OL,7,Fcontinues to build its work
OL,8,Finternationally, this visit is an
OL,9,Fopportunity to connect the Shaping Us
OL,10,FFramework with leading global
OL,11,Fapproaches, and to highlight a shared
OL,12,Funderstanding, that it is in these
OL,13,Fearly years, through the natural world
OL,14,Fand the warmth of human connection,
OL,15,Fthat we begin to lay the foundations
OL,16,Ffor a resilient and healthy future."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
