PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FThe centre was founded by Kate in 2021
OL,7,Fto raise awareness of the importance
OL,8,Fof early years experiences in shaping
OL,9,Fsociety over the long term, and to
OL,10,Fcommission research.
OL,12,FThe announcement coincides with a
OL,13,Fvisit by Kate to the University of
OL,14,FEast London on Wednesday for the
OL,15,Flaunch of the centre's new resource
OL,16,Ffor people working with babies, young
OL,17,Fchildren and their families.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FIn its foreword, Kate writes: "While
OL,7,Four society often focuses on academic
OL,8,For physical milestones, research
OL,9,Fconsistently shows that it is our
OL,10,Fearliest relationships, experiences
OL,11,Fand environments which lay the
OL,12,Ffoundations for our future health and
OL,13,Fhappiness.
OL,15,F"The quality of our connections - with
OL,16,Fourselves, with others and with the
OL,17,Fworld around us - shapes how safe we
OL,18,Ffeel, how we relate, and how we
OL,19,Fprocess experiences throughout our
OL,20,Flives."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
