OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FSince then, she has gradually returned
OL,7,Fto royal duties, including supporting
OL,8,Fthe King at state visits to the UK,
OL,9,Fand last month joined the royal family
OL,10,Fto mark the 100th anniversary of the
OL,11,Flate Queen Elizabeth II's birth, and
OL,12,Fmade a solo appearance at the Cenotaph
OL,13,Fon Anzac Day.
OL,15,FThe Waleses' last major lengthy tour
OL,16,Ftogether was their controversial trip
OL,17,Fto the Caribbean in March 2022 to
OL,18,Fcelebrate the Platinum Jubilee, before
OL,19,Fthey spent three days in Boston in
OL,20,FDecember 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778080262
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales to resume overseas
OL,4,Croyal duties with solo trip to Italy
OL,6,FWilliam had expressed his hopes in
OL,7,FNovember 2024 that his wife would
OL,8,Fbegin to join him again on overseas
OL,9,Ftours, saying: "I think hopefully
OL,10,FCatherine will be doing a bit more
OL,11,Fnext year, so we'll have some more
OL,12,Ftrips maybe lined up."
OL,14,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,15,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,16,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,17,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
